00:38:17.720 --> 00:38:19.764
all social media led,
all grassroots led.

00:38:19.764 --> 00:38:21.930
And the government wasn't
ever going to do anything.

00:38:21.930 --> 00:38:24.747
So they would love to
control us, I think.

00:38:24.747 --> 00:38:27.080
So I think, yeah, you have
to take the good with the bad

00:38:27.080 --> 00:38:27.788
as well, I think.

00:38:27.788 --> 00:38:29.940
You know, it would
be nice if we were

00:38:29.940 --> 00:38:31.790
a bit politer to each
other on social media

00:38:31.790 --> 00:38:32.630
and on the internet.

00:38:32.630 --> 00:38:34.467
But I don't see that happening.

00:38:34.467 --> 00:38:36.050
JULIEN FINLAY: Do
you see it happening

00:38:36.050 --> 00:38:38.570
on yourself, whenever
