00:41:41.930 --> 00:41:43.427
and the stuff he comes out with.

00:41:43.427 --> 00:41:44.010
It's because--

00:41:44.010 --> 00:41:45.890
JULIEN FINLAY: He was
banned for one hour.

00:41:45.890 --> 00:41:46.220
FINLAY WILSON: One day.

