00:42:10.100 --> 00:42:12.014
And it's quite right wing.

00:42:12.014 --> 00:42:13.430
But they're happy
to go with this,

00:42:13.430 --> 00:42:14.756
because it generates clicks.

00:42:14.756 --> 00:42:16.630
It generates people
looking at their content.

00:42:16.630 --> 00:42:18.710
And it generates
advertising revenue.

00:42:18.710 --> 00:42:19.800
JULIEN FINLAY: I'll go
