00:42:31.580 --> 00:42:33.620
into the schools'
curriculum, which

00:42:33.620 --> 00:42:36.740
seems to be the best idea
to educate people early on.

00:42:36.740 --> 00:42:40.010
But then there seems to
be this huge discrepancy

00:42:40.010 --> 00:42:43.760
between that idea and
