00:42:43.760 --> 00:42:46.981
court proceedings against what
is perceived as hate speech

00:42:46.981 --> 00:42:47.480
online.

00:42:47.480 --> 00:42:48.980
I think there was a comedian.

00:42:48.980 --> 00:42:50.840
He was convicted
