00:42:50.840 --> 00:42:54.200
made that Jewish people
might feel is distasteful.

00:42:54.200 --> 00:42:55.970
And at the same time,
you say whatever

00:42:55.970 --> 00:42:58.430
you reported that
happened to an actual life

00:42:58.430 --> 00:43:03.560
outside of any online
interactions, people damaging

00:43:03.560 --> 00:43:06.290
the tires of the
